title: Dino Crisis (Xperia Play PlayStation Pocket Game)
description:
DINO CRISIS

Custom game for the Sony Ericsom Xperia Play

Instructions:

1- Copy the file com.sony.playstation.SLUS_00922.apk to anywhere on the sd card of your Xperia Play.

2- Copy the folder named com.sony.playstation.SLUS_00922 to your sd card Android/data folder.

3- On your Xperia Play, install the game using the file com.sony.playstation.SLUS_00922.apk.

Observations:

- Works perfectly on Xperia Play with Android 2.3.4
- May presents some problems with the audio of dialogues.

Enjoy.
